{"tid":1874932,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[醫生爆料］衛生署安排隔離營患者自己搭車到急症求醫","createTime":"2020-02-11T12:58:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-11T16:47:36.000Z","uid":305252,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"dce22de9f8c281cbc7e59345bb946d6cbde5b2df","tid":1874932,"uid":305252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T12:58:32.000Z","msg":"衛生署安排<span style=\"color: red;\">有症狀</span>隔離營患者<span style=\"color: red;\">自己搭車</span>到我間急症室睇症<br />\n（被分類為高危的紅手帶患者除外，有專車，不過未知點分類）<br />\n<br />\n佢途中大可以去打個邊爐、唱個K先過來，既可享受放監生活，亦可傳播祖國大愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過最大機會都係去各大醫院嘅飯堂或者醫院附近食肆<br />\n<br />\n即係話我依頭送完佢入負壓隔離病房，果頭食返佢口水尾<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n真係和味濃<br />\n<br />\n利申：急症醫生<br />\n有興趣可以睇下我D舊post<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/og94zyG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fog94zyG.png&h=0eeac43f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"76375dc9c0f680e911937a522639b3128928d18b","tid":1874932,"uid":207792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T13:00:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abf8cef9e30d69518333901ea93ddfdd9ed91e5b","tid":1874932,"uid":305252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dce22de9f8c281cbc7e59345bb946d6cbde5b2df","tid":1874932,"uid":305252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T12:58:32.000Z","msg":"衛生署安排<span style=\"color: red;\">有症狀</span>隔離營患者<span style=\"color: red;\">自己搭車</span>到我間急症室睇症<br />\n（被分類為高危的紅手帶患者除外，有專車，不過未知點分類）<br />\n<br />\n佢途中大可以去打個邊爐、唱個K先過來，既可享受放監生活，亦可傳播祖國大愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過最大機會都係去各大醫院嘅飯堂或者醫院附近食肆<br />\n<br />\n即係話我依頭送完佢入負壓隔離病房，果頭食返佢口水尾<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/w